The '''''Fury''''' is the flagship of [[Stannis Baratheon]]'s fleet. Its name is a reference to the words of [[House Baratheon]], &quot;Ours is the Fury&quot;.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[House Baratheon (Complete Guide to Westeros)]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

The ''Fury'' takes part in the [[Battle of the Blackwater]], with Stannis as its captain and Ser [[Imry Florent]] as the King's first mate.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Blackwater (episode)|Blackwater]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

